commit.message: Update phpstan baselines

CsvResultSetUtils: Query results in bulk..

..if there's no limit imposed. PDO runs queries in buffered mode
by default. Fetching without a limit needlessly increases the risk
to require more memory than available.

JsonResultSetUtils: Query results in bulk..

..if there's no limit imposed. PDO runs queries in buffered mode
by default. Fetching without a limit needlessly increases the risk
to require more memory than available.
Controller: Properly reset the default query limit during exports
Use separate result sets when exporting hosts/services
Transfer implementation of JsonResultSet and CsvResultSet to separate traits

Transform custom variable filters as late as possible

not be done by default anymore

migrate/search-url: Prevent further false-positives

See included comment

fixes #969

Only qualify base columns during quick searches

All other columns are already qualified relative to the
base model. This is usually sufficient because qualification
is only required if applied to a query, which isn't happening
at this stage.
